title: Johnny Winter - Live at Sweden Rock Festival 2009 [FM] [FLAC]
description:
Johnny Winter recorded live at Sweden Rock Festival 2009.

FM broadcast received on a Revox B780 and recorded to a Revox B77 reel to reel.
Played back and recorded to computer with Audacity via external A/D.

The track has been trimmed, normalized and exported as FLAC (24/96), nothing else.

Tracklist:
01 She Likes To Boogie Real Low
02 Miss Ann
03 Black Jack
04 I'm Tore Down
05 Lone Wolf
06 Red House
07 Bony Moronie
08 It's All Over Now
09 The Mojo Boogie
10 Highway 61 Revisited

Runtime: 55m 23s

NOTE: Swedish radio announcer speaks a few times during some intros.
